  "keyFeatures": [
    "Visual node-based canvas for designing automated tests (no code required)",
    "Real-time test execution with integrated screencast via WebSocket/CDP",
    "Playwright code generation from visual flows and interaction recording",
    "30+ built-in node types: actions, assertions, control flow, and lifecycle hooks",
    "Device emulation (mobile, tablet, desktop) with locale, timezone, and geolocation",
    "Parallel test execution with configurable workers, retries, and timeouts",
    "HTML test reports with screenshots and per-node results",
    "Visual element picker for building CSS/XPath selectors interactively",
    "JWT-based authentication with Admin and User roles",
    "SQLite by default with Turso/libsql and PostgreSQL support",
    "One-command launch via npx or Docker"
  ],
